       crosstool-NG. In fact, it is *VERY* dangerous to run as root, as
@@ -56,7 +55,7 @@ config ALLOW_BUILD_AS_ROOT
       (ad libitum)
 
 config ALLOW_BUILD_AS_ROOT_SURE
